{"tid":2167761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"四個 #公務員 團體發聯合聲明，支持政府提出公務員試用期間，若參與非法公眾活動被捕，可被解僱。","createTime":"2020-08-21T10:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T10:52:41.000Z","uid":241764,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0d07d8944cabfc0068da29590e00b67993bf3c99","tid":2167761,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"政府人員協會、香港公務員總工會、國家行政學院香港同學會，以及香港特區政府公務人員聯會，發表聯合聲明指，公務員在試用期間，因參與針對政府的非法公眾活動而被捕和起訴，可被解僱，做法符合基本法、港區國安法及公務員守則，並稱公務員守則要求公務員必須堅守法治，對在任行政長官及政府完全忠誠。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=402606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402606&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=0c9f25da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402606&h=fb4d966a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=402606</a>"},{"pid":"156c830a8d23544477fa782477566be880e9bd3b","tid":2167761,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"918db20ff6e8693cb9edec982b7ace2e04c15e06","tid":2167761,"uid":181321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:12:54.000Z","msg":"我唔信perm咗果班俾人拉唔會解僱囉"},{"pid":"e947db09e772d9df367923bec040f8dcfcb0f4d0","tid":2167761,"uid":3860,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:13:42.000Z","msg":"邊個會入呢D公會 <br />\n唔幫自己會員 笑死"},{"pid":"05399e4c5b864a1064b2655e7e843b943cde934e","tid":2167761,"uid":305358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:21:40.000Z","msg":"政府部門使唔使搞咁多公會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個Dept.幾個公會咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810744c6a45a9896205746177ab34a948b550c1e","tid":2167761,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2